Viyaviya na mweye walume, kaleni na wake zenu kwa kuvimanya kuwa wawo ni walume hawadaha kuwa na luholozi fana mweye, ivo mwizahokela hamwe nawo chitumetume cha unovu wa Mulungu woukwing'higwa ugima. Muvimanye kuwa habule munhu yoyodaha kulemesa nhosa zenu.
Mwolonda nifambule, mweye wose muwe na magesa yamwega, muwe na ubazi, na mwanduse fana ndugu vimulondeka, muwe na uhuwilo na wanyendanyenda.
Sekemulihe vihile kwa vihile, hebu ugoni kwa ugoni, mbali mulekelele kutenda vihile. Kwaviya Mulungu kamtanga mweye muladi mutende ivo, na munayamweda mate.
Kwaviya Yamaandiko Yelile yolonga, "Munhu yoyose yoyolonda ugima na kuwona siku zinogile, yaileme lulimi lwake sekeulonge yehile, na iviya yaleke kulonga uvwizi.
Munhu iyo kolondeka yaileke yehile na yatende yanogile, yolonda tindiwalo na kuiwinza.
Kwaviya meso ya Mndewa yowagesa wanhu wanogile, na magutwi yake yotegeleza nhosa zawo. Mbali Mndewa kowabamanya wanhu wowotenda yehile."
Yelihi yonda yawatende vihile mweye vonda muwe na ludabwa lwa kutenda yanogile?
Mbali hata fana muhagazigwa kwa ichimu cha kutenda yanogile, Mulungu kamtemelani mate. "Sekemudumbe, wala sekemudumbe."
Mbali mumtogole Chilisito Mndewa muna imizoyo yenu. Siku zose mukale goya kumwidika munhu yoyose yondayamulongeleni chimu cha uhuwilo womuulile, ditendeni ivo kwa unyendanyenda na ukulu,
Mbali muilonde kwa moyo unogile, muladi waja wowabedala na wowowabedala kusang'hanila yanogile kusang'hana yenu munogile muna Chilisito Mkombola, wawone chinyala kwaviya wawo womuliga.
