Wawo ni waja wowakalile wolema kumuhulika Mulungu chipindi chiya Mulungu viyakalile kogozela kwiza kwa Nuhu. Chipindi icho, Mulungu kakala kogozela kuzenga safina. Wanhu wadodo muhala wowokomboligwe muna safina iyo, wanhu wanane, wawo wakomboligwa kulawa muna dilamba kulu ng'hani.
